snippet.textDisplay:
She came in a indian singing contest as i remember her outfit. 

Her vocals are too similar throughout the whole thing. If you hear sufi/islamic reciters pray this sufi kalam by Sultan Bahoo they pray it with all their power. There should be emphasis during the verses which this lacks

The music is on point though which is the most important thing!
